#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.52"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.52:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.52:0.2"
msgid "5. Dhammikavagga"
msgstr "5. About Dhammika"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Khattiyasutta"
msgstr "52. Aristocrats"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: jāṇussoṇi → jāṇusoṇi (mr)
msgctxt "an6.52:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"And then the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi went up to the Buddha, and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "an6.52:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.363"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Khattiyā, bho gotama, kiṃadhippāyā, kiṃupavicārā, kiṃadhiṭṭhānā, "
"kiṃabhinivesā, kiṃpariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Aristocrats, Master Gotama, have what as their ambition? What is their "
"preoccupation? What are they dedicated to? What do they insist on? What is "
"their ultimate goal?”"

msgctxt "an6.52:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Khattiyā kho, brāhmaṇa, bhogādhippāyā paññūpavicārā balādhiṭṭhānā "
"pathavībhinivesā issariyapariyosānā”ti. (1)"
msgstr ""
"“Aristocrats, brahmin, have wealth as their ambition. They’re preoccupied "
"with wisdom. They’re dedicated to power. They insist on territory. Their "
"ultimate goal is sovereignty.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Brāhmaṇā pana, bho gotama, kiṃadhippāyā, kiṃupavicārā, kiṃadhiṭṭhānā, "
"kiṃabhinivesā, kiṃpariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Brahmins, Master Gotama, have what as their ambition? What is their "
"preoccupation? What are they dedicated to? What do they insist on? What is "
"their ultimate goal?”"

msgctxt "an6.52:3.2"
msgid ""
"“Brāhmaṇā kho, brāhmaṇa, bhogādhippāyā paññūpavicārā mantādhiṭṭhānā "
"yaññābhinivesā brahmalokapariyosānā”ti. (2)"
msgstr ""
"“Brahmins have wealth as their ambition. They’re preoccupied with wisdom. "
"They’re dedicated to the hymns. They insist on sacrifice. Their ultimate "
"goal is the Brahmā realm.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Gahapatikā pana, bho gotama, kiṃadhippāyā, kiṃupavicārā, kiṃadhiṭṭhānā, "
"kiṃabhinivesā, kiṃpariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Householders, Master Gotama, have what as their ambition? What is their "
"preoccupation? What are they dedicated to? What do they insist on? What is "
"their ultimate goal?”"

msgctxt "an6.52:4.2"
msgid ""
"“Gahapatikā kho, brāhmaṇa, bhogādhippāyā paññūpavicārā sippādhiṭṭhānā "
"kammantābhinivesā niṭṭhitakammantapariyosānā”ti. (3)"
msgstr ""
"“Householders have wealth as their ambition. They’re preoccupied with "
"wisdom. They’re dedicated to their profession. They insist on work. Their "
"ultimate goal is to complete their work.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Itthī pana, bho gotama, kiṃadhippāyā, kiṃupavicārā, kiṃadhiṭṭhānā, "
"kiṃabhinivesā, kiṃpariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Women, Master Gotama, have what as their ambition? What is their "
"preoccupation? What are they dedicated to? What do they insist on? What is "
"their ultimate goal?”"

msgctxt "an6.52:5.2"
msgid ""
"“Itthī kho, brāhmaṇa, purisādhippāyā alaṅkārūpavicārā puttādhiṭṭhānā "
"asapattībhinivesā issariyapariyosānā”ti. (4)"
msgstr ""
"“Women have a man as their ambition. They’re preoccupied with adornments. "
"They’re dedicated to their children. They insist on being without a co-wife. "
"Their ultimate goal is sovereignty.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:6.1"
msgid ""
"“Corā pana, bho gotama, kiṃadhippāyā, kiṃupavicārā, kiṃadhiṭṭhānā, "
"kiṃabhinivesā, kiṃpariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Bandits, Master Gotama, have what as their ambition? What is their "
"preoccupation? What are they dedicated to? What do they insist on? What is "
"their ultimate goal?”"

# For satha “crafty” vs. sattha “sword” see BB’s note. MA 149 confirms the reading “sword”: 所立以刀. There’s another parallel at EA 37.8, but the phrasing is looser and I can’t determine if there’s an exact parallel of this phrase.
msgctxt "an6.52:6.2"
msgid ""
"“Corā kho, brāhmaṇa, ādānādhippāyā gahanūpavicārā satthādhiṭṭhānā "
"andhakārābhinivesā adassanapariyosānā”ti. (5)"
msgstr ""
"“Bandits have theft as their ambition. They’re preoccupied with a hiding "
"place. They’re dedicated to their sword. They insist on darkness. Their "
"ultimate goal is invisibility.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:7.1"
msgid ""
"“Samaṇā pana, bho gotama, kiṃadhippāyā, kiṃupavicārā, kiṃadhiṭṭhānā, "
"kiṃabhinivesā, kiṃpariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Ascetics, Master Gotama, have what as their ambition? What is their "
"preoccupation? What are they dedicated to? What do they insist on? What is "
"their ultimate goal?”"

#. VAR: ākiñcaññābhinivesā → akiñcanābhinivesā (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "an6.52:7.2"
msgid ""
"“Samaṇā kho, brāhmaṇa, khantisoraccādhippāyā paññūpavicārā sīlādhiṭṭhānā "
"ākiñcaññābhinivesā nibbānapariyosānā”ti. (6)"
msgstr ""
"“Ascetics have patience and gentleness as their ambition. They’re "
"preoccupied with wisdom. They’re dedicated to ethical conduct. They insist "
"on owning nothing. Their ultimate goal is extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.364"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an6.52:8.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ, bho gotama, abbhutaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, Master Gotama, it’s amazing!"

msgctxt "an6.52:8.2"
msgid ""
"Khattiyānampi bhavaṃ gotamo jānāti adhippāyañca upavicārañca adhiṭṭhānañca "
"abhinivesañca pariyosānañca. Brāhmaṇānampi bhavaṃ gotamo jānāti … pe … "
"gahapatīnampi bhavaṃ gotamo jānāti … itthīnampi bhavaṃ gotamo jānāti … "
"corānampi bhavaṃ gotamo jānāti … samaṇānampi bhavaṃ gotamo jānāti "
"adhippāyañca upavicārañca adhiṭṭhānañca abhinivesañca pariyosānañca."
msgstr ""
"Master Gotama knows the ambition, preoccupation, dedication, insistence, and "
"ultimate goal of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, women, bandits, and "
"ascetics."

msgctxt "an6.52:8.3"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "an6.52:8.4"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.52:8.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
